## Bounded contexts (do not mix)

| Context | Code paths | External system |
| ------- | ---------- | --------------- |
| **Platform / Identity** | `routes/v1/auth`, `accounts`, `sellers`, `risk-analysts`, `admins`, `payers`; `domain/account`, `domain/seller` | Internal DB only |
| **Receivables** | `routes/v1/receivables`, `receivable-internal`; `domain/receivable` | Internal DB only |
| **Ramp** | `routes/v1/ramp`, `integrations/etherfuse` | Etherfuse FX API |
| **Registry** | `routes/v1/trade-bills`, `domain/tradeBill`, `integrations/registry`, `generated/` | Soroban `TradeBillRegistry` |

Cross-context correlation: explicit IDs in DB only — no tight coupling in code.

